Link: <https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/v1/ngsi-ld-core-context.jsonld>; rel="http://www.w3.org/ns/json-ld#context"; type="application/ld+json"

{
    "LP1": {
        "languageMap": {
            "en": "yes",
            "es": "si"
        }
    },
    "R1": "urn:E1",
    "id": "urn:E1",
    "type": "T"
}


04. PATCH E1, deleting R1 using the special string "urn:ngsi-ld:null" for object, and without type=Relationship present
=======================================================================================================================
